description: Truly one of a kind  Penthouse with  two decks including a private roof deck with panoramic water views  and 2 deeded parking spaces.    This custom crafted unit has an open floor plan with a chef's kitchen designed with an island  finished with marble countertops, custom cabinets,  and Viking appliances.   Along with the high end finishes this unit has hardwood floors throughout, California  closets,  central air, in unit laundry and a gas line on the deck for grilling.    The king size master bedroom includes a large walk in closet and en suite bath with a steam shower and a double vanity.    2nd bedroom is large enough for a queen bed and desk.
